### English Title:
Kuwait's Interior Ministry Arrests Illegal Resident for Assaulting Security Officer

### English Text Summary:
The Kuwaiti Interior Ministry announced the arrest of an illegal resident who deliberately ran over a security officer in front of the Al-Fintas police station early Thursday and fled the scene. Thanks to the quick response of security personnel, the suspect was apprehended by the Ahmadi support patrols, who used force to stop him. Upon searching, authorities found drugs and a firearm in his possession. The ministry emphasized its commitment to not tolerate any threats against security personnel or public safety and praised the vigilance of the patrol officers. The suspect and the seized items were referred to the relevant authorities for legal action.

